OL,3,CNHS doctor urges Government to
OL,4,Cevacuate injured dad from Gaza
OL,6,FA doctor from is urging the government
OL,7,Fto help evacuate his father from Gaza
OL,8,Fso that he can undergo life-saving
OL,9,Fsurgery.
OL,11,FDr Mohammed Balousha's father, Khaled,
OL,12,Fwas left with a traumatic brain injury
OL,13,Fafter he was struck with shrapnel
OL,14,Foutside a shelter in the Southern Gaza
OL,15,FStrip on 9 December.
OL,17,FThe 61-year-old Palestinian is being
OL,18,Ftreated in a makeshift field hospital,
OL,19,Fbut his condition is deteriorating and
OL,20,Fdoctors are unable to perform the
OL,21,Fneurosurgery he needs.
