OL,3,CNHS doctor urges Government to
OL,4,Cevacuate injured dad from Gaza
OL,6,FDr Balousha, 32, has raised enough
OL,7,Fmoney for his father to have the vital
OL,8,Foperation in Egypt and has contacted
OL,9,Fseveral agencies and charities in an
OL,10,Funsuccessful attempt to secure his
OL,11,Ffather's evacuation.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News: "The first thing
OL,14,Fthat comes to mind is I'm not there,
OL,15,Fand I'm a doctor.
OL,17,F"If I don't help, nobody else will be
OL,18,Fable to and I know that he will not
OL,19,Fsurvive. So it's a matter of life and
OL,20,Fdeath, isn't it?
