OL,3,CNHS doctor urges Government to
OL,4,Cevacuate injured dad from Gaza
OL,6,F"Worry, fear, concern - I think I'm
OL,7,Fbeyond that. Everything has stopped."
OL,9,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,10,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,11,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,12,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,14,FKhaled was injured while trying to buy
OL,15,Ffood for his young grandchildren. His
OL,16,Ffamily had been sheltering in a school
OL,17,Fbecause of the ongoing conflict
OL,18,Fbetween Israeli and Palestinian forces.
