OL,4,Cevacuate injured dad from Gaza
OL,6,FDr Balousha, who is training to become
OL,7,Fa trauma surgeon, is asking the
OL,8,FBritish Government to help facilitate
OL,9,Fhis father's move through the Rafah
OL,10,FCrossing into Egypt.
OL,12,FHowever, he said the UK authorities
OL,13,Fhave refused because neither of them
OL,14,Fare British citizens.
OL,16,FHe added: "I have a connection with
OL,17,Fthe UK and my father has a connection
OL,18,Fwith the UK.
