OL,3,CNHS doctor urges Government to
OL,4,Cevacuate injured dad from Gaza
OL,6,F"My father is the person who worked
OL,7,Fall his life to make me a doctor, who
OL,8,Ftoday works here in the NHS.
OL,10,F"Everyone should put all politics
OL,11,Faside. There is a person who needs an
OL,12,Fintervention and the intervention is
OL,13,Fthere. Just make it happen."
OL,15,FDr Balousha has now set up a petition
OL,16,Fthat's been signed by more than 2,000
OL,17,Fpeople in the hopes of making the
OL,18,FGovernment reconsider.
